{"tid":1380402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叫撚咗你班人咪再影相 尋日仲有影義士post ig story","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:30:37.000Z","uid":6097,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a63b897f8c7d7a8161aab0fa621ab566b510a8","tid":1380402,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"如果Facebook 自行審查nowtv新聞係真<br />\n證明香港代理嘅social media 已經唔可信<br />\n<br />\n所以咪叫大家咪撚係現場影相打卡囉<br />\n做人低調少少啦 <br />\n<br />\nIg都係fb管<br />\n我以為現場除咗記者 唔影相係共識嚟<br />\n<br />\n到咗尋日都仲有人影影影 ig story見撚哂樣<br />\n<br />\n返到去見到曾經直播都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打少陣卡會死？<br />\n你去觀光呀？出攝展？<br />\n去過一定要畀全世界知？<br />\n低調啦屌 <br />\n<br />\n你畀狗查 畀人兇兩兇 就淆到仆街解鎖<br />\n累埋其他義士真係多得你唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實尋晚真係嬲到仆街<br />\n好想屌死佢 但記得講過對同路人客氣啲<br />\n<br />\n老老實實 下次再見到咁點先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9095b6a11ad9349f966294a27137af28956f355","tid":1380402,"uid":6097,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"你班打卡撚除咗負評同開live拎手指公<br />\n仲識做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16944db00b2c552b7f33c62929daac21bc91da23","tid":1380402,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:22:49.000Z","msg":"sosial media 一向唔信<br />\n尤其 facebook"},{"pid":"1fe8adb688576d87473046dda4cd8bbfafd27bc5","tid":1380402,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac5ed5e53838a68fd092946c1476b986c